  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/84b90771845633085aef6cc6239c4185.webp?t=1768323001\" width=600 height=57 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Snowsquall Grip </strong>is a short horror/thriller game with PSX/Retro aesthetics where the player gets lost amid a sudden snowstorm.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/3852feb2eeb28a5eed3a6418e204fa91.poster.avif?t=1768323001\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/3852feb2eeb28a5eed3a6418e204fa91.webm?t=1768323001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/3852feb2eeb28a5eed3a6418e204fa91.mp4?t=1768323001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Primary: Walking simulator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intuitive Physics-Based Item Interaction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Straightforward Puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Low on Jumpscares: Emphasis on the Atmospheric Exploration</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/72c37e97994714bf1cb0b2a2605ad8ae.poster.avif?t=1768323001\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/72c37e97994714bf1cb0b2a2605ad8ae.webm?t=1768323001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/72c37e97994714bf1cb0b2a2605ad8ae.mp4?t=1768323001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/8f4e7120d923138ba80a03931ce7bf03.poster.avif?t=1768323001\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/8f4e7120d923138ba80a03931ce7bf03.webm?t=1768323001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/8f4e7120d923138ba80a03931ce7bf03.mp4?t=1768323001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Emergency Scenario</strong>: Trapped in an unforgiving snowstorm in the style of PSX horror games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Inventory, Only Instinct</strong>: With no inventory to rely on, every essential item for survival must be manually grabbed and utilized with precision.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Battle the Elements</strong>: Fight against the biting cold to maintain your sanity, as you navigate through the relentless snowsquall.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncover Creepy Secrets</strong>: Piece together the eerie mysteries lurking within the storm's icy grip.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Escape or Perish</strong>: Will you summon the courage to confront the unknown and find your way out, or succumb to the icy depths of this frozen nightmare, forever lost in its chilling embrace?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/e2d5c7931e6c0e23921e13e2d1d991fc.poster.avif?t=1768323001\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/e2d5c7931e6c0e23921e13e2d1d991fc.webm?t=1768323001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/e2d5c7931e6c0e23921e13e2d1d991fc.mp4?t=1768323001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE STORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In their relentless pursuit of the ultimate energy source, scientists from Modern-City, under the leadership of The Supreme One, established a hidden facility to study a mysterious radiation seeping from beneath a thick ice layer, far from civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maintaining this operation demands a constant supply of special energy batteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your task is to deliver these batteries. What starts as a routine delivery mission quickly unravels into a journey that sheds light on the dark secrets of the elusive energy known in the future as \"Re.Surs\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/b87008248c83b2ac379d9b1425e24d85.poster.avif?t=1768323001\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/b87008248c83b2ac379d9b1425e24d85.webm?t=1768323001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/b87008248c83b2ac379d9b1425e24d85.mp4?t=1768323001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GAME IS PART OF THE \"RE.SURS UNIVERSE\" GAME SERIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[RE.SURS] [PLASTOMORPHOSIS]</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/84b90771845633085aef6cc6239c4185.webp?t=1768323001\" width=600 height=57 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Snowsquall Grip </strong>is a short horror/thriller game with PSX/Retro aesthetics where the player gets lost amid a sudden snowstorm.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/3852feb2eeb28a5eed3a6418e204fa91.poster.avif?t=1768323001\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/3852feb2eeb28a5eed3a6418e204fa91.webm?t=1768323001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/3852feb2eeb28a5eed3a6418e204fa91.mp4?t=1768323001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Primary: Walking simulator</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intuitive Physics-Based Item Interaction</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Straightforward Puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Low on Jumpscares: Emphasis on the Atmospheric Exploration</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extras/72c37e97994714bf1cb0b2a2605ad8ae.poster.avif?t=1768323001\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000420/extr